{
  "texts": [
    "Adenovirus particles were purified from 293T cell lysates by polyethylene glycol precipitation, CsCl gradient centrifugation, and gel filtration column chromatography.",
    "Adenovirus preparations were quantified by A 260 measurements (OD 260 1.0 = ~10 12 virus particles).",
    "Purified adenovirus was stored at -80 °C in small aliquots.",
    "U373 cells were infected with 4 × 10 9 adenovirus particles/ml by direct addition of purified virus to the culture medium.",
    "U373 cells were plated into 4-well chamber slides (5 × 10 4 cells/well)."
  ]
}